70
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,039
to stop this carnage.

71
00:04:03,392 --> 00:04:04,319
In the end,

72
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,759
Wang Chongyang prevailed

73
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,488
