74
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,520
the Nine Yin True Sutra.

75
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:11,960
Nine Yin True Sutra.

76
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,360
Path to invincibility.

77
