102
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,560
Drink by yourself.

103
00:05:03,872 --> 00:05:04,879
Alright.

104
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:05,856
Go.

105
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,680
Sir.

106
