114
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,120
If your father could see

115
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,360
what you've become from the afterworld,

116
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,759
he'd be heartbroken.

117
00:06:18,944 --> 00:06:19,879
Shameless.

118
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:20,768
You...

119
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,000
Suffer for the rest

120
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,328
