127
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:53,984
You like her?

128
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,424
She's yours.

129
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,639
You're so lucky.

130
00:07:12,576 --> 00:07:13,560
Hey, pretty.

131
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,528
Relax.

132
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:15,600
I'll be gentle.

133
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,279
I won't hurt you.

134
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,560
Trying to run?

135
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,352
Get lost.

136
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:35,072
Let go.

137
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,928
Keep her alive.

138
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,776
Keep running.

139
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,128
Get her.

140
00:09:17,472 --> 00:09:18,480
Get her.

141
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,328
- Understood!
- Understood!

142
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:25,600
- Get her!
- Get her!

143
