Wait.

144
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,240
Have you seen a woman in red?

145
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,720
No.

146
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,679
No?

147
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,880
Come on out.

148
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,072
Thank you.

149
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:12,480
Yah!

150
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:26,879
She's right inside.

151
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:29,159
Search thoroughly.

152
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,136
I want her alive.

153
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,480
You scheming viper!

154
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:34,879
I'll kill you!

155
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:52,832
Over there.

156
00:12:52,919 --> 00:12:53,760
Get her.

157
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:54,639
Hurry.

158
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,616
Get her.

159
00:12:56,928 --> 00:12:57,824
Hurry.

160
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,928
Over here.

161
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,072
Hurry.

162
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:16,704
Hurry.

163
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,464
Go.

