359
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,320
No.

360
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:45,960
Wait for me at the dock.

361
00:30:47,359 --> 00:30:48,256
Master.

362
00:31:24,559 --> 00:31:26,119
Huang Yaoshi.

363
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:28,400
One of the Five Greats.

364
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,664
So invincible.

365
00:31:30,640 --> 00:31:31,599
