417
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,504
I'm not going.

418
00:36:01,639 --> 00:36:02,688
Knock it off.

419
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,719
Master will be here.

420
00:36:06,519 --> 00:36:07,760
- You go.
- You go.

421
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:09,280
Go on.

422
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,176
Hurry up.

423
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,280
I am Qu Lingfeng.

424
00:36:16,384 --> 00:36:17,320
Excuse me...

425
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:18,280
Young lady.

426
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,159
How old are you?

427
00:36:20,288 --> 00:36:21,239
Who asks

428
00:36:21,239 --> 00:36:22,639
