429
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:23,776
Right?

430
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:25,800
Seniority is based on age here.

431
00:36:26,119 --> 00:36:27,079
Mianfeng cares about it.

432
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:28,352
Exactly.

433
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:29,696
Fair enough.

434
00:36:29,984 --> 00:36:30,976
Miss,

435
00:36:31,119 --> 00:36:31,960
