444
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:46,944
Qu Lingfeng.

445
00:36:47,648 --> 00:36:48,719
He is

446
00:36:48,719 --> 00:36:49,800
the second eldest.

447
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,679
Chen Xuanfeng.

448
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:52,800
I am

449
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:54,000
supposed to rank fourth

