00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,679
I'm Master's most accomplished disciple,

452
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:57,856
Lu Chengfeng.

453
00:36:59,904 --> 00:37:00,896
He is

454
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:01,880
the youngest.

455
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,360
Wu Mianfeng.

456
00:37:04,639 --> 00:37:05,960
Might I ask your name?

457
00:37:06,679 --> 00:37:07,584
Mei Ruohua.

458
00:37:08,519 --> 00:37:09,639
Mei Ruohua.

459
00:37:11,079 --> 00:37:12,159
All of us bear "feng"

460
00:37:12,639 --> 00:37:13,599
in our names.

461
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,816
I presume Master

462
00:37:15,159 --> 00:37:16,440
