470
00:37:30,119 --> 00:37:31,360
You were slacking off.

471
00:37:32,384 --> 00:37:33,320
Enough.

472
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,304
Master is here.

473
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:36,960
- Master.
- Master.

474
00:37:39,239 --> 00:37:40,096
You met?

475
00:37:40,639 --> 00:37:41,519
- Yes.
- Yes.

476
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:45,000
I, Mei Ruohua from Pingjiang Prefecture,

477
00:37:45,280 --> 00:37:46,679
asked to be a disciple

478
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,719
of Huang Yaoshi

479
00:37:48,039 --> 00:37:49,400
to learn martial arts.

480
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:51,840
You kindly took me in.

481
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,599
I shall respect you,

482
00:37:54,360 --> 00:37:55,239
heed your teachings,

483
00:37:55,599 --> 00:37:56,440
