488
00:38:02,239 --> 00:38:03,239
Follow your heart.

489
00:38:03,559 --> 00:38:04,639
Roam freely.

490
00:38:05,079 --> 00:38:06,320
May you find yourself

491
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,960
and start anew

492
00:38:09,360 --> 00:38:10,519
on Taohua Island,

493
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,159
and let go of the past.

494
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:13,824
Understood.

495
00:38:25,599 --> 00:38:26,480
Winds of Dao

496
00:38:27,079 --> 00:38:28,119
