497
00:38:29,639 --> 00:38:30,800
I roam beyond worldly cares.

498
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,912
Henceforth,

499
00:38:35,519 --> 00:38:36,440
you shall be called

500
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:39,559
