509
00:39:11,719 --> 00:39:12,576
Out.

510
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,144
Let's go.

511
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:15,880
Your master says

512
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,088
that you lack inner energy.

513
00:39:17,440 --> 00:39:18,639
Ask Mianfeng

514
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:20,840
for three specially-made

515
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:21,760
Nine-Flower Dew Pills

516
00:39:22,679 --> 00:39:23,519
to strengthen

517
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,800
