526
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:57,840
In a second.

527
00:40:04,719 --> 00:40:06,480
What do you think about our master's

528
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:07,776
new disciple?

529
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:10,000
We finally have

530
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:11,000
a female disciple.

531
00:40:11,519 --> 00:40:13,079
I thought she'd be a sweet

532
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:14,000
little girl.

533
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,000
But she

534
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:16,239
