535
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,440
I find her quite unique.

536
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,376
Especially the way

537
00:40:21,719 --> 00:40:22,920
she looks at people.

538
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:25,000
Cold, stubborn,

539
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,239
