540
00:40:28,039 --> 00:40:28,920
Lingfeng.

541
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,519
Don't tell me you're in love with her.

542
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,736
Nonsense.

543
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,480
Master will break your legs.

544
00:40:35,639 --> 00:40:36,599
She might be

545
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:39,599
