00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,208
Not necessarily.

582
00:41:58,679 --> 00:42:00,159
My parents didn't fight in the war.

583
00:42:01,159 --> 00:42:03,400
Maybe her family was also

584
00:42:04,559 --> 00:42:06,079
Master's old acquaintances?

585
00:42:06,079 --> 00:42:07,000
No more wild guesses.

586
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:09,000
Now that she's here,

587
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,080
we're all family.

588
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:11,808
Exactly.

589
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,280
Stop guessing.

