594
00:42:57,888 --> 00:43:01,632
♪Extinguished by frost-laden winds♪

595
00:43:01,632 --> 00:43:06,848
♪Now I see this longing
bears a sinful debt♪

596
00:43:07,968 --> 00:43:10,752
♪And I finally perceive♪

597
00:43:11,648 --> 00:43:15,232
♪That heartbreak spins its own cocoon♪

598
00:43:15,232 --> 00:43:16,928
♪Binding us together♪

599
00:43:17,184 --> 00:43:21,664
♪With our earthly desires
surging skyward♪

600
00:43:21,664 --> 00:43:24,352
♪I watch dreams shatter like snowflakes♪

601
00:43:24,832 --> 00:43:27,840
♪Scattering through the fleeting sky♪

602
00:43:28,352 --> 00:43:32,864
♪From this moment, all my yearning♪

603
00:43:32,864 --> 00:43:35,392
♪Turns to ashes and vanishes♪

604
00:43:35,392 --> 00:43:38,944
♪You're the thought rooted in my soul♪

605
00:43:38,944 --> 00:43:42,272
♪An endless thread of fate♪

606
00:43:42,272 --> 00:43:44,608
♪You're the string in the wind♪

607
00:43:44,608 --> 00:43:49,056
♪Pulling me through this lifetime♪

608
00:43:49,312 --> 00:43:52,480
♪If all love in this world is cursed♪

609
00:43:53,088 --> 00:43:55,392
♪Then forgive my foolishness♪

610
00:43:56,672 --> 00:43:59,584
♪Leaving myself no escape♪

611
00:43:59,584 --> 00:44:02,336
♪And granting no time for regret♪

612
00:44:02,912 --> 00:44:06,240
♪You're the chaos I embrace♪

613
00:44:06,240 --> 00:44:09,568
♪My unyielding obsession♪

614
00:44:09,568 --> 00:44:11,808
♪You're the unclimbable peak♪

615
00:44:11,808 --> 00:44:16,384
♪Far beyond the clouds♪

616
00:44:16,736 --> 00:44:19,936
♪Even if opposed by all♪

617
00:44:19,936 --> 00:44:23,136
♪This fervor can't be relieved♪

618
00:44:23,392 --> 00:44:25,440
♪I'll never surrender♪

619
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:29,440
♪Let me be lost in this madness♪
